text: In my opinion, I don’t think it’s likely. Professors have a limited amount of hours allocated for tutors and TAs to grade the material, host office hours, proctor tests/quizzes, etc.

I’d also like to add that my mom got into an accident on the freeway in our first FJ and rolled 3 times. She walked out of the car with only bruising and some cuts. This is the reason we immediately got another. It kept her safe when she needed it most.
